# Plan: Add PulseBoard Channel Plugin

## Context

OpenClaw is a multi-channel messaging framework with a plugin architecture. Each messaging platform (IRC, Nostr, Telegram, etc.) lives as a workspace package under `extensions/`. This plan adds a new **fictional** `pulseboard` channel plugin — a real-time bulletin board platform — following the exact same structure and SDK contracts used by existing channel plugins.

The task creates **7 new files only** under `extensions/pulseboard/`. No existing files are modified.

---

## Architecture Overview (from codebase research)

Each channel plugin follows this layout:
```
extensions/<id>/
  package.json               # npm package + openclaw metadata block
  openclaw.plugin.json       # plugin manifest (id, channels, configSchema)
  index.ts                   # defineChannelPluginEntry() entry point
  setup-entry.ts             # defineSetupPluginEntry() for setup-only loading
  src/
    types.ts                 # account/config/message TypeScript interfaces
    runtime.ts               # createPluginRuntimeStore() singleton
    channel.ts               # createChatChannelPlugin() — the ChannelPlugin object
```

`pnpm-workspace.yaml` already includes `extensions/*`, so pulseboard will be auto-discovered.

---

## Key SDK Imports (verified in source)

| Symbol | Import path |
|---|---|
| `createPluginRuntimeStore` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/runtime-store` |
| `defineChannelPluginEntry`, `defineSetupPluginEntry` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` |
| `createChatChannelPlugin`, `getChatChannelMeta` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` |
| `attachChannelToResult` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` |
| `PluginRuntime` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` |
| `ChannelPlugin` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core` |

---

## Files to Create

### 1. `extensions/pulseboard/package.json`

Standard npm package with `"type": "module"` and the `openclaw` block. No runtime dependencies (fictional platform). Pattern: IRC/Nostr `package.json`.

```json
{
  "name": "@openclaw/pulseboard",
  "version": "2026.4.1-beta.1",
  "description": "OpenClaw PulseBoard channel plugin",
  "type": "module",
  "devDependencies": {
    "openclaw": "workspace:*"
  },
  "peerDependencies": {
    "openclaw": ">=2026.4.1-beta.1"
  },
  "peerDependenciesMeta": {
    "openclaw": { "optional": true }
  },
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": ["./index.ts"],
    "setupEntry": "./setup-entry.ts",
    "channel": {
      "id": "pulseboard",
      "label": "PulseBoard",
