Thin runtime store using `createPluginRuntimeStore`. Exports `getPulseBoardRuntime` and `setPulseBoardRuntime` using destructuring-and-rename. Pattern: Telegram's `runtime.ts` (uses `PluginRuntime` from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/core`).

```typescript
